<li>National Adoption Month</li>
<li>Day of the Dead (November 1-2)</li>
<li>Forget-Me-Not Day (November 10)</li>
<li>Women Entrepreneurs Day (November 19)</li>
<li>Transgender Day of Rememberance (November 20)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>December
<ul>
